name: Senior #8 - Fei Hong
description:
Fei Hong is a 75-year-old former shaolin master who enjoys sitting, breaking bottles and reading hate comments online. He is smart and meticulous, but can also be very cowardly and a bit inconsiderate.

He defines himself as heteroflexible. He finished his training and then left Shaolin Temple. He has a severe phobia of meatballs, and is secretly obsessed with Elon Musk.
